title: Country Ass Whuppin' (2012) (digital) (Minutemen Annika) cbr
description:
The stories have one thing in common-- they are all about people in the south kickin' ass or getting their ass kicked! Enjoy both tall-tales and true stories, told by some of the best in the business; including Jason Aaron (X-MEN), Sean Patrick Flanery (BOONDOCK SAINTS), Rebekah Isaacs (ANGEL & FAITH), Nathan Edmondson (THE ACTIVITY) and many more. Don't miss this celebration of southern culture, while having fun and helping those in need.

enjoy
